snippet.title: Minecraft LIVE - September 2025
snippet.description:
New game drops! Developers! More!

Minecraft LIVE is our own super special show that gives you the inside info on everything happening in the world of Minecraft! 

We‚Äôre updating vanilla Minecraft with multiple game drops per year, so we now host two of these shows to cover all the new features. Every episode includes fresh info from our developers, the inside scoop on unannounced upcoming game drops, and more! 

After the broadcast, stay tuned in for the Deep Dig After Show where our developers and guests show off the new features, often resulting in chaos. Vu Bui will return as host and attempt to keep things running smoothly. Good luck to that guy!

American Sign Language: https://www.youtube.com/live/W3uQA_unm0I
British Sign Language: https://youtube.com/live/ZygMYm2sx5U
Audio Descriptions: https://youtube.com/live/DoXrLv__PAY

Check out Minecraft.net for more information!

snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Dawn of War IV ‚Äì "Back to War" In-Engine Trailer | PC Gaming Show Tokyo Direct
snippet.description:
Here‚Äôs your official look into the next evolution of the iconic real-time strategy franchise with Warhammer 40,000: Dawn of War IV!
First revealed during PC Gaming Show: Tokyo Direct, this new trailer has been captured entirely from in-engine gameplay. 

Many years after the events of Dawn of War: Dark Crusade, Kronus burns as Space Marines of the Blood Ravens Chapter and their Adeptus Mechanicus allies clash with brutal Ork hordes. With victory almost certain, a new threat emerges: the Necrons. As this new faction overwhelms the battlefield, the Imperium must rebuild and grow their forces if they hope to stand a chance. 

Whether you‚Äôre a long-time fan of the series or brand new to the world of Dawn of War, this new trailer, captured entirely in-engine, provides a more detailed look at what to expect with exciting gameplay, action-packed cinematics, and a taste of the war-torn future that awaits.

At last, back to war! 
---

Warhammer 40,000: Dawn of War IV releases on Steam in 2026!

snippet.title: MIBR vs. NRG ‚Äî VALORANT Champions Paris ‚Äî Playoffs Stage
snippet.description:
Welcome to the climax of the 2025 VALORANT Champions Tour! The biggest stage in VALORANT is ready, the lights of Paris are shining, and the countdown has begun. Following a season of historic rivalries, epic comebacks, and unforgettable moments, the world‚Äôs top teams now gather at Champions Paris.

From September 12 to October 5, the journey continues through Group Stage and Playoffs before the epic conclusion at the Grand Final with the crowning of the next World Champion. The Group Stage will feature 16 teams spread across four groups, with each group hosting one team from VALORANT's four International Leagues. In this stage, teams will battle through a double elimination format, advancing two teams out of each group. The 8 teams who make it out will be randomly seeded into a double elimination bracket, with teams from the same group placed on opposite sides of the bracket. Teams will compete through Best-of-3 matches until the final 2 matches which will be a Best-of-5. The last team standing will claim the title of VALORANT World Champion!

We‚Äôre proud to work with our fantastic partners throughout 2025: AWS, Coinbase, EWC, HyperX, Mastercard, OMEN, Red Bull, Secretlab, and Verizon.

Make sure to follow the official VALORANT Esports social channels for additional information:

snippet.title: How I "DIED" on a Hardcore Minecraft SMP
snippet.description:
i got banned on the unstable smp

How I "DIED" on a Hardcore Minecraft SMP

inspired by @4CVIT's naked and afraid series!

thank you to:  @Boosfer @loppezz @FlameFragsMC eggchan @LettuceK @Twirps as well as all of the capital city guards and merchant city players!

music from:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9UKPs9ZisfhMJdalnETLRg (tons of my music is by AZALI so check him out!)
https://www.youtube.com/@nombra101 (song during the first flame fight!)

This is a Minecraft video recorded in the Unstable Universe that is staged for story-telling purposes; any more staged videos I upload will have a disclaimer in the description saying that they are also staged. Also, a lot of the game mechanics/glitches/redstone discussed in Unstable SMP videos are unique to the Unstable SMP / Unstable Universe and either will not work the same/do not exist in vanilla Minecraft. 

music also from: official minecraft soundtrack, official elder scrolls soundtracks, epidemic sound (https://www.epidemicsound.com), storyblocks (https://www.storyblocks.com), artlist (https://artlist.io), soundstripe (https://www.soundstripe.com), fesliyan studios (https://www.fesliyanstudios.com/royalty-free-music), and envato (https://elements.envato.com/)

snippet.title: Avatar: Fire and Ash | New Trailer
snippet.description:
This world is much deeper than you imagine. Watch the brand-new trailer for Avatar: Fire and Ash and experience it in theatres December 19th.

Also, don‚Äôt miss Avatar: The Way of Water back on the big screen in 3D for one week only, starting October 3rd.

snippet.title: Amos Raber - Closely Disconnected (Official Music Video) Ft Conrad Fisher #andygriffithshow #country
snippet.description:
Closely Disconnected was written by Amos Raber and Conrad Fisher - the music video was filmed in and around Shipshewana Indiana.

This music video is Sponsored by DAVIS MUSIC SHOP in Shipshewana! 
Check out their website and make sure to stop by when visiting Shipshewana! 
https://davismusicshop.com

Filmed & Edited by Lucas Wilson
Special thanks to Nate Hershberger for the super cool 1967 Pontiac Firebird!
Also special thanks to Joas Bontrager for the pond location!

Special thanks to our friends for being in the video!
Harvey & Mary Raber
John Yutzy 
Galen & Ilene Yoder
Karl & Anna Lambright 
Levi & Miriam Bontrager
Marvin & Arlene Hostetler
Vernon & Abby

John & Susan Yoder family

Youtube Music:  https://music.youtube.com/channel/UCHGp4XRsRHidsifDh3S9TxQ?si=7nuyxLrcwoXpCRbr

Apple Music:  https://music.apple.com/us/artist/amos-margaret-raber/710109188

Facebook:  https://www.facebook.com/bygraceministry

Instagram:  https://www.instagram.com/amosraberfam/

Website:  https://www.bygraceministry.com


Lyrics
I drove into town the other day, and what I saw, I'll have to say 
Warmed my heart and put a smile on my face
There were people standing around together, they talked about life and a little'bout the weather
It reminded me of when the world had a different pace

My mind went back to 1930 when the roads were narrow and the streets were dirty
People didn't seem too be in such a big 'ole rush
Now everyone, or so it seems, is busy staring at their screens
People don't take the time to talk as much

Chorus:
It seems we're closely disconnected, everybody's been affected 
By the gismos and the gadgets that our modern world can boast 
Oh, if we don't pay attention we'll lose all sense and direction 
Don't be closely disconnected from the ones you love the most

But I sure do like my new smart phone, it makes it awfully easy to call back home 
I can check on mom and dad any time I please
Yea, I'll admit, it's really something, I can run my world with the push of a button 
But sometimes it feels like my phone runs me

So learn to quilt, or read a book, fly a kite, or bait a hook 
And don't just do it for the Instagram reel
You can go back home and see your folks, sing some songs and crack some jokes
You might be surprised at how good you feel.
